this into the story of "Madam

00:01:35.550 --> 00:01:38.196
Secretary" and the CBS show.

00:01:38.196 --> 00:01:39.570
And what I decided,
the direction

00:01:39.570 --> 00:01:42.510
I decided to take this in was
to be more about the two of you

00:01:42.510 --> 00:01:48.690
as a duo, as a pair, as a
producing team, because--

