Catch "The Story of
Us" with Morgan Freeman

00:46:07.110 --> 00:46:10.830
on National Geographic on
October 11, which is very soon,

00:46:10.830 --> 00:46:11.420
of course.

00:46:11.420 --> 00:46:13.050
And then season 4
of "Madam Secretary"

00:46:13.050 --> 00:46:15.210
premieres this
Sunday, October 8.

00:46:15.210 --> 00:46:16.740
Everyone please go watch it.

00:46:16.740 --> 00:46:18.480
Help me thank them
for showing up today.

